room_title: Escape room "Mind-Boggling" by American Escape Rooms in Orlando
room_description: Your team find themselves in the hidden and mysterious recesses of your minds. Will chaos or order rule your thoughts and actions? Will you find light or darkness inside? Sterile emptiness on one side, hectic movement of life on the other side. These two distinct territories are linked together by a series of interesting, challenging and fun puzzles which you can only solve if you work together. Are you ready to overcome the perplexing puzzles to set yourselves free from the boundaries of your minds within sixty minutes?
